### Event Logs API Testing

# @host = http://localhost:8080
@host = http://event-logs.onlyspans.ru

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/actuator/health

### Prometheus Metrics
GET {{host}}/actuator/prometheus

### Get Settings
GET {{host}}/settings

### Update Settings
PUT {{host}}/settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "retentionPeriodDays": 45,
  "maxExportSize": 12000
}

### Search All Events
GET {{host}}/events

### Search Events with Filters
GET {{host}}/events?user=test-user&category=USER_ACTION&page=0&size=20

### Search Events by Date Range
GET {{host}}/events?startDate=2026-01-01T00:00:00Z&endDate=2026-01-31T23:59:59Z

### Search Events by Project and Environment
GET {{host}}/events?project=test-project&environment=development

### Search Events with Sorting
GET {{host}}/events?sortBy=timestamp&sortOrder=desc&size=10

### Export Events to CSV
GET {{host}}/events/export
Content-Type: application/json